## Testing Contract

Issue #3: Entry URLs must be valid absolute URLs

```clojure
;; MUST return :invalid-url-host error
(validate-entry {:id "https://wal.shsite/event/" ...})
;; 'wal.shsite' looks like typo for 'wal.sh/site'

;; MUST accept URN identifiers
(validate-entry {:id "urn:uuid:123..." ...})
;; => no URL error
```

## Boundaries

- Uses lambdaisland/uri for parsing
- urn:uuid:* always valid for atom:id
- TLD heuristics may have false positives

